import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import { Container, Row } from "../GlobalStyle";
import * as H from "./style";
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome';
import { faBars } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';

function Header() {
    return(
        <>
            <Container>
                <Row spaceBetween alignItemsCenter>
                    <H.LogoDiv>
                        <H.Logo alt="site-logo" src="https://movephysiotherapy.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Move_P_F_Logo-Black_Blue-removebg-preview.png"></H.Logo>
                    </H.LogoDiv>
                    <H.MenuWrapper>
                        <H.MenuList>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/">Home</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/about">About</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/services">Services</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/conditions">Conditions</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/blog">Blog</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/projects">Projects</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/contact">Contact</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                        </H.MenuList>
                    </H.MenuWrapper>
                    <H.MenuButton>
                        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={ faBars } />
                    </H.MenuButton>
                </Row>
                <Row>
                    <H.MenuWrapper>
                        <H.MobileMenuList>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/">Home</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/about">About</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/services">Services</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/conditions">Conditions</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/blog">Blog</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/projects">Projects</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                            <H.MenuItem>
                                <Link to="/contact">Contact</Link>
                            </H.MenuItem>
                        </H.MobileMenuList>
                    </H.MenuWrapper>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </>
    );
}

export default Header;
